{"tid":968360,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"其實張學友首李香蘭係講咩？","createTime":"2019-01-04T07:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T13:54:34.000Z","uid":215894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"eea06462627905bc08fb191c1203009684b265b6","tid":968360,"uid":215894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:32:21.000Z","msg":"個人都幾鐘意隻歌既旋律，但係歌詞究竟係講緊咩？ 有冇才子解答<br />\n<br />\n惱春風　我心因何惱春風<br />\n說不出　借酒相送<br />\n夜雨凍　雨點透射到照片中<br />\n回頭似是夢　無法彈動　迷住凝望你　褪色照片中<br />\n<br />\n啊　像花雖未紅　如冰雖不凍　卻像有無數說話　可惜我聽不懂<br />\n啊　是杯酒漸濃　或我心真空　何以感震動<br />\n<br />\n照片中　哪可以投照片中<br />\n盼找到　時間裂縫<br />\n夜放縱　告知我難尋你芳蹤<br />\n回頭也是夢　仍似被動　逃避凝望你　卻深印腦中"},{"pid":"ae97f45368e299e658c8ce77e55f31d6ab4aadaf","tid":968360,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:35:14.000Z","msg":"李香琴我就識"},{"pid":"d5fcbf7a340457ffaf6a1d8b675690486dc873dd","tid":968360,"uid":555,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:36:38.000Z","msg":"就唱你老母李香蘭"},{"pid":"f593b4c8b974413559b5d6bb4e7c14a533fc78d4","tid":968360,"uid":29982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:43:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9D%8E%E9%A6%99%E8%98%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E9%25A6%2599%25E8%2598%25AD&d=JS6%2Bb5RV8sKIbXK7uPI%2FUL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=0e4f6a03\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9D%8E%E9%A6%99%E8%98%AD</a>"},{"pid":"972182f07df4f1bb10d3704162c04e2a61cb4afc","tid":968360,"uid":14833,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:47:17.000Z","msg":"成首講你亞媽係漢奸"},{"pid":"ffc13094d00b150b2f487ac90d0319c7b43cdb50","tid":968360,"uid":187719,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XbDXL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XbDXL4.jpg&h=f9364d62&s=